main event: On the evening of September 9, 1965, the witness saw a triangular-shaped, brilliantly lighted object move silently and rapidly across the sky near Walpole, Massachusetts.
interesting points: The object moved at a speed quite rapid compared to the oval-shaped objects the witness had seen earlier on September 4, 1965.
The object had a beautiful blue-green color.
The witness had also seen two similar oval-shaped objects on September 4, 1965, which moved slowly across the sky in a circular path.
The witness would like further technical explanation on these sightings.
The report indicates that this was part of Project Blue Book, a U.S. Air Force program to investigate unidentified flying objects.
